Madagaskaran Tazovaldkund alajagase 22 regionha (provincijha) ([[malagasin kel'|malagas.]] ''faritra''), kudambad alajagase departamentoihe (niid om 112) ([[malagasin kel'|malagas.]] ''departemanta''), a ned — kommunihe ([[malagasin kel'|malagas.]] ''kaominina'') (niid om 1395). Kommunad edemba alajagase 17,544 ''fokontany'':he<ref>[http://www.instat.mg/pdf/carto_poly.pdf Presentation des resultats de la cartographie numerique en preparation du troisieme recensement generale de la population et de l'habitation. — Institut nationale de la statistique (INSTAT, instat.mg), Government of Madagascar.] {{ref-fr}}</ref>. Regionad ühtenzoittas 6 avtonomižhe agjaha (provincijha) ([[malagasin kel'|malagas.]] ''faritany mizakatena'').

== Eläjad ==
Madagaskaras elädas [[malagasijalaižed]].

Madagaskaran toižed sured lidnad (enamba 100 tuh. rist., vl 2012<ref>[http://archive.is/20121209103455/http://www.world-gazetteer.com/wg.php?x=&men=gcis&lng=en&des=gamelan&srt=npan&col=adfhimoq&msz=1500&geo=-137 Madagascar: largest cities and towns and statistics of their population. — World-gazetteer.com] {{ref-en}}</ref>, surembaspäi penembha): [[Tuamasin]], [[Ancirabe]], [[Fianarancua]], [[Mahadzang]], [[Tuliar]].

